{"word":"βρῶμα","slug":"βρῶμα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>βρῶμα, ατος, τό</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:βιβρώσκω\">βιβρώσκω</a></el>] <b><i>food</i> <a href='B:470 14:15'>Mt 14:15</a></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ al.\">al.</a>; by extension, of spiritual nourishment <b><a href='B:500 4:34'>J 4:34</a>; <a href='B:530 3:2'>1 Cor 3:2</a>.</b> In<b> 10:3</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:βρῶμα\">βρῶμα</a></el> refers to material food, but the qualifier <el>πνευματιϰόν</el> specifies that the real significance of <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:βρῶμα\">βρῶμα</a></el> is to be discerned at a higher level. <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:βρύω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:βρώσιμος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}